 MochiKit
 --------

 The directory "src/static/js/MochiKit/" contains files from the MochiKit
 javascript library.  This is used for some of the user interface code sent to
 the user's browser.  It is under the following terms:
 
  Copyright 2005 Bob Ippolito <bob@redivi.com>. This program is dual-licensed
  free software; you can redistribute it and/or modify it under the terms of
  the MIT License or the Academic Free License v2.1.
